    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>The Other Mother</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Lisa Hunter-Epstein letter faults member of lesbian couple in child custody dispute for trying to cut other mother out of children's lives (July 25 Peggy Orenstein article)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>'E.'' is setting a bad precedent by showing her daughters that it's O.K. to cut a mother figure out of their lives. Given how angry they may be about this when they're older, I suspect that someday the girls will take the lesson to heart, and suddenly ''E.'' may find her own calls unanswered, her own letters returned, her own gifts unopened.</p>
        <p>Lisa Hunter Epstein  New York</p>
      </block>
